# <type>(<optional scope>): <short summary in imperative mood>
#
# Types: feat | fix | docs | style | refactor | perf | test | build | ci | chore | revert
# Scopes (examples): cli | template | ci | docs
#
# - Subject ≤ 72 chars, no trailing period
# - Blank line, then body wrapping at ~72 chars (why, not how)
# - Footer: BREAKING CHANGE: …  or  Refs: #123
#
# Changelog: for feat/fix/perf/BREAKING, update CHANGELOG.md in the same commit or PR.
#
# Examples:
#   feat(cli): support --domain ml non-interactive create
#   fix(template): hide blog section when posts empty
#   docs: add PR and commit message templates
